    <div class="documentBody">
        
        <div>
            <p>Lubna Jaffery Fjell was appointed State Secretary in the Ministry of Culture on 23 October 2009. Lubna Jaffery Fjell’s previous position was that of Political Adviser to the ministers Bjarne Håkon Hanssen and Dag Terje Andersen in the Ministry of Labour and Social Inclusion.&nbsp;</p>
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="546" colspan="2">
<p>&nbsp;<strong>Work experience:</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="121">
<p>2008-2009</p></td>
<td valign="top" width="425">
<p>Political Adviser to the ministers Bjarne Håkon Hanssen and Dag Terje Andersen in the Ministry of Labour and Social Inclusion.</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="121">
<p>2007</p></td>
<td valign="top" width="425">
<p>Adviser for SINTEF Technology and Society, Department of Global Praxis</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="121">
<p>2000</p></td>
<td valign="top" width="425">
<p>Political Adviser for the Norwegian Labour Youth (AUF)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="121">
<p>&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top" width="425">
<p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="546" colspan="2">
<p><strong>Education:</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="121">
<p>2005–2007</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p></td>
<td valign="top" width="425">
<p>Master of Administration and Organization Theory, University of Bergen</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="121">
<p>2004</p></td>
<td valign="top" width="425">
<p>Undergraduate degree in Comparative Politics, University of Bergen</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="121">
<p>2002-2003</p></td>
<td valign="top" width="425">
<p>Undergraduate studies in Comparative Politics, University of Bergen</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="121">
<p>2001-2002</p></td>
<td valign="top" width="425">
<p>Undergraduate studies in Public Law, University of Bergen</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="121">
